      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――とある音楽番組の収録後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After a music program recording.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1699.9999324999999,
          "startTime": 1.6999999325
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。今日の収録、凄く良かったよ\nトリエルは安定感があるから安心して見ていられるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. Today’s recording was great.\nTRINITYAiLE is so stable‚ it’s reassuring to watch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7333333254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5203623176
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n安定感があると評価していただけるのは嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much.\nI’m glad you think our performance is stable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.2999999921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "常にベストなパフォーマンスが出来るように\n心がけて、日々練習をしていますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To deliver the best performance in any situations‚\nI strive to practice every day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1333333254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5852148414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "練習に裏打ちされた自信か……瑠依らしいな\n瑠依は昔からそんな風に堂々としていたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Confidence backed by practice… That’s so like you‚ Rui.\nHave you always been so confident?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9999999921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "私だって\n最初からなんでもうまく出来た訳じゃありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not really.\nI wasn’t good at everything from the beginning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9333333254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.3853257696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "デビュー当時は気負って空回りして\n失敗することもよくありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I first debuted‚ I was so eager that I often made mistakes‚\nand even failed many times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1999977033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依が空回りする姿なんて想像もつかないが……\n一体どんな失敗をしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t imagine you making mistakes…\nWhat kind of mistakes did you make?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6999994834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.1506766835
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "それは……\n恥ずかしいので言いたくありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well…\nIt’s embarrassing‚ so I don’t want to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4666661501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.3585022806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "頑張った結果なら、何も恥ずかしがることは\nないと思うが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's the result of your hard work‚ so I think\nyou don't have to be embarrassed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1333353599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_08_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "私だって見栄を張りたい時もあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sometimes‚ I want to look good too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7874365527,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}